  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7127741">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7127741/" class="title-link">美的历史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7127741"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/76184330/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u76184330-64.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/76184330/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">店长K</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-10-13"
      class="main-meta">2014-10-13 22:28:11</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7127741_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  美是什么？优雅、华丽、高贵、精巧、丰饶、别致，这些词语皆可以是美带给我们的感觉。经过大自然打磨的玉石虽是粗糙，但那种拙朴的力量仍不失美感；若被匠师精雕细琢了一番，则褪去原始的粗糙，显得灵气逼人，亦让人赞叹这巧夺天工。这是自然之美与艺术之美的不同，是现代为美...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7127741/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">16有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7127741_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7127741_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





